reviews.review_text: 3 & a half star show, 5 star sound The two high points of the show for me are Brown Eyed Women and Space. Usually I don't care about Space, but I don't really care about this show in general. It's good. No really crazy licks more than usual, they didn't really pull anything out, but good. If you're a fan of Built to Last as I am, you've rarely heard a well-done rendition, and this one is not an exception. The sound quality is awesome.
